title: KEEP FAILING AND YOU WILL SUCCEED
itunes:title: KEEP FAILING AND YOU WILL SUCCEED

description:
This is a motivational speech for those facing failure, whether in school, business, success, or life. Keep failing. Learn from your mistakes. But Never Give Up. Winners Don't Quit.
